WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  'Queens' is a Workbench game where you try to place 8 Queens on
a chessboard, in such a way that none are in line with each other,
either horizontally, vertically or diagonally.

  You play by clicking on an empty space where you want to place
a Queen, and a queen-like icon will appear there. If there are
other Queens in line, they will be removed from the board...

  Have fun!

